title: American Flagg v1 (001 - 050 + v2 01 - 12) (1983 - 1989)
description:
American Flagg v1 (001 - 050 + v2 01 - 12) (1983 - 1989)


The year is 2032. Corruption, prostitution, subliminal images and cameras are everywhere, from the top of what's left of the American government down to the sleaziest pit you can imagine. Assigned to keep law and order are the Plexus Rangers. Committed to bringing the American dream "back together" is Rueben Flagg. This is his story
